<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>VIIB Ocean Memories</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f5fbff;
    color:#1b2a41;
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,40,80,.7),rgba(0,80,140,.7)),
    url("22064.jpg");
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
}

.hero-content h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero-content p{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:25px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    background:#00c2ff;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#0097c8;
    transform:translateY(-3px);
}

/* SECTION */
section{
    padding:70px 8%;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
    color:#005f99;
    font-size:2rem;
}

/* INFO */
.info-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:25px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-5px);
}

.card h3{
    color:#0077b6;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* ABOUT */
.about{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#dff6ff,#f7fcff);
    border-radius:25px;
    padding:35px;
    line-height:1.9;
    text-align:center;
}

/* VISI MISI */
.vm{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.box{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.box ul{
    padding-left:20px;
    line-height:1.9;
}

/* HOBBY */
.hobby{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:20px;
}

.hobby-card{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    width:250px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.hobby-card span{
    font-size:3rem;
}

/* MOTTO */
.motto{
    text-align:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0077b6,#00b4d8);
    color:white;
    padding:50px 20px;
    border-radius:25px;
}

.motto h2{
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
    background:#003049;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:768px){

.hero-content h1{
    font-size:2.2rem;
}

.hero-content p{
    font-size:1rem;
}

.section-title{
    font-size:1.7rem;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
<div class="hero-content">
<h1>🌊 VIIB Ocean Memories</h1>
<p>
Selamat datang di VIIB Ocean Memories, tempat di mana setiap siswa menjadi bagian
dari perjalanan yang penuh cerita, persahabatan, dan kenangan indah.
</p>

<a href="#tentang" class="btn">Jelajahi Kelas</a>
</div>
</section>

<!-- INFORMASI -->
<section>
<h2 class="section-title">👨‍🎓 Informasi Kelas</h2>

<div class="info-grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Jumlah Siswa</h3>
<p><b>35 Siswa</b></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>👨‍🏫 Wali Kelas</h3>
<p><b>Pak Dheden</b></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📚 Kelas</h3>
<p><b>VIIB</b></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🌊 Tema</h3>
<p><b>Ocean Memories</b></p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>💙 Semangat</h3>
<p><b>Kompak, Kreatif, dan Berprestasi</b></p>
